1. create helm chart
   -> helm create apache-helm

2. install helm for different namespace dev and test
   -> helm install dev-apache ./apache-helm/ -n dev-apache --create-namespace
   -> helm install test-apache ./apache-helm/ -n test-apache --create-namespace

3. if we edit conif in any one namespace (like in test)
   -> vi apache-helm/values.yaml  (change the values ex: increase replicas)
   -> vi apache-helm/Chart.yaml  ( edit version )

4 upgrade the config using upgrade command.
   -> helm upgrade test-apache apache-helm/ -n test-apache
